:32:30.000Z","msg":"捶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"推，自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7b4c4038bf0a28662b1edafb5c0950aaf42e17","tid":1625132,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d5e7caaf4e812696016d9e170d29a4f82529349d","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"推 10/10"},{"pid":"0dbb03a3959707ed156cbed58d60e54f1d2da89c","tid":1625132,"uid":117819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔好比林奠亂咁解讀"},{"pid":"8695ee6b842f886fedfc23d902de84ab313bbe80","tid":1625132,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b375af62dfc5bf3cee8395a4754060a19a7606","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"(From tg group 破解政府心戰室)<br />\n<br />\n見到好多post鬧法官唔頒禁制令，誤解判詞話因為法庭唔信蒙面法會令示威者行動升級，所以要做俾法庭睇。<br />\n<br />\n但法庭其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">完全冇講過</span></span>啲咁嘅野。 (利申: law撚, 喺法庭現場)<br />\n<br />\n其實個官基本上係講：<br />\n<br />\n1. 根據案例，除非被覆核嘅條例好好好明顯地違憲，法庭唔會喺正式覆核前頒臨時禁制令。詳見：梁頌恆案para 13：<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfi/2018/1869.html?stem=&amp;synonyms=&amp;query=(2018%205%20HKC%20138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fcgi-bin%2Fsinodisp%2Feng%2Fhk%2Fcases%2Fhkcfi%2F2018%2F1869.html%3Fstem%3D%26synonyms%3D%26query%3D%282018%25205%2520HKC%2520138&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=305318ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfi/2018/1869.html?stem=&amp;synonyms=&amp;query=(2018%205%20HKC%20138</a>)%20OR%20ncotherjcitationtitles(2018%205%20HKC%20138)<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢次審訊只係關乎臨時禁制令，而申請人未有獲得法庭司法覆核嘅許可 (因為司法覆核嘅許可星期二先審)，而根據Practice Direction SL3 第10段，法庭一般都唔會係呢個階段頒臨時禁制令。詳見PD SL3, para 10：<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/pd/pdcontent.jsp?pdn=PDSL3.htm&amp;lang=CH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fpd%2Fpdcontent.jsp%3Fpdn%3DPDSL3.htm%26lang%3DCH&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=5d0bf020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/pd/pdcontent.jsp?pdn=PDSL3.htm&amp;lang=CH</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 因此，雖然法庭初步認為司法覆核有得拗，但現階段都唔會頒臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n由此可以見到個官<span style=\"color: red;\">冇(未)講過條例有冇問題，亦冇睇死手足唔會升級</span>，而最早下星期先開始討論緊急法同禁蒙面法違唔違憲，<span style=\"color: red;\">搞法庭對我地冇好處</span>，只會：<br />\n<br />\n1. 令我地<span style=\"color: red;\">失去外國戰線</span>: 班外國人權法治撚會覺得我地同班popo同港共政府一樣，唔尊重法治；<br />\n<br />\n2. 令<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭內部分化</span>: 唔少手足對法庭有情意結，搞法庭未必人人支持。<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪點解冇一份新聞有講裁決理由 (可能班記者聽唔明)。如果有人亂咁喺度帶風向，成件事就好危險。所以小弟奉勸大家：<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈，千祈，千祈唔好俾人誤導，唔好衝動行事！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後想帶出一個重點: <span style=\"color: red;\">我地冇輸到</span>，因為個官都有提過呢單<span style=\"color: red;\">司法覆核有得拗，只係唔係今日拗</span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n留意郭榮鏗同長毛都會幫手入稟JR，大家唔好自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n更多法律分析及實用錦囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwarroom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwarroom&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a4690ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwarroom</a><br />\nBy 個腦生左係屎忽度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac6c9f425c34157842940de72222f2170624dcfc","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dbb03a3959707ed156cbed58d60e54f1d2da89c","tid":1625132,"uid":117819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔好比林奠亂咁解讀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"八婆亂咁講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d64e5919db3d9f644702f3c672242f0387083f8","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960c9678089cc3d09fb16bc6d4b5e769e6af3055","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a78769c5201a8ac60f6874cc60a571e5124b8be","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb0ab4c2271040129a5a98a0c722730168e0e43","tid":1625132,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"837e7e30eba373443d11cf20d73ce35dfda71d1e","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed33441672e33c81e63e1f03bbb962d8eef20ad0","tid":1625132,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46e83501d69730ad668177bdaa46c560302e16e4","tid":1625132,"uid":250127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5201631927d88132394454ff8a94ae95e5a2c03a","tid":1625132,"uid":77443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:09:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6d0140596426e151deb3153f41da0f2854c7c0a2","tid":1625132,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a114824